00:39:30,361 --> 00:39:32,701
There are thunders and lightnings.

541
00:39:34,333 --> 00:39:35,673
It's quite loud.

542
00:39:38,451 --> 00:39:39,381
Are you scared?

543
00:39:39,781 --> 00:39:40,801
I'm not scared.

544
00:39:52,579 --> 00:39:53,729
I'm a little scared.

545
00:39:58,822 --> 00:39:59,879
Forget it.

546
00:39:59,920 --> 00:40:01,340
I'm going back to my room.

547
00:40:03,241 --> 00:40:04,115
Let's go to the living room.

548
00:40:04,156 --> 00:40:05,376
I can't sleep anyway.

549
00:40:14,442 --> 00:40:15,582
Liang Mu Ze.

550
00:40:17,158 --> 00:40:18,618
Are you having insomnia again?

551
00:40:18,961 --> 00:40:20,421
If you can't fall asleep,

552
00:40:21,018 --> 00:40:23,118
you can try meditation.

553
00:40:24,293 --> 00:40:25,433
Firstly,

554
00:40:25,865 --> 00:40:27,605
close your eyes.

555
00:40:29,233 --> 00:40:31,173
Relax your body.

556
00:40:33,789 --> 00:40:35,529
Then, starting counting.

557
00:40:36,915 --> 00:40:43,910
One, two, three, four, five.

558
00:40:50,928 --> 00:40:52,148
Inhale.

559
00:40:53,918 --> 00:40:55,458
Count to five.

560
00:40:59,030 --> 00:41:00,810
Exhale.

561
00:41:04,399 --> 00:41:06,259
Inhale.

562
00:41:09,659 --> 00:41:11,439
Exhale.

563
00:41:21,511 --> 00:41:22,576
No matter what,

564
00:41:22,617 --> 00:41:24,246
ever since we share a house,

565
00:41:24,287 --> 00:41:25,567
my mum doesn't have to worry

566
00:41:25,608 --> 00:41:26,708
about my safety anymore.

567
00:41:27,870 --> 00:41:29,120
In that case,

568
00:41:29,725 --> 00:41:31,825
he's not completely useless.

569
00:41:32,863 --> 00:41:35,413
Then why are you picking on him?

570
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:37,786
Please know your position.

571
00:41:37,836 --> 00:41:38,876
He's your landlord.

572
00:41:38,917 --> 00:41:40,127
He's not your husband.

573
00:41:40,252 --> 00:41:42,726
As long as he doesn't install
a hidden camera to peek on you...

574
00:41:42,767 --> 00:41:44,447
or doesn't sell his house away,

575
00:41:44,488 --> 00:41:47,138
all the other things are not important.

576
00:41:47,972 --> 00:41:48,852
Of course.

577
00:41:49,257 --> 00:41:50,882
If you plan to move in with him,

578
00:41:50,923 --> 00:41:53,143
then we shall adjust the standards.

579
00:41:53,704 --> 00:41:55,604
I don't plan to move in with him.

580
00:41:55,858 --> 00:41:56,776
Do you know?

581
00:41:56,817 --> 00:41:58,846
Everything that you just complained...

582
00:41:58,887 --> 00:42:01,077
sounded as if both of you
are a little couple...

583
00:42:01,118 --> 00:42:02,538
trying to get along with each other.

584
00:42:03,374 --> 00:42:04,714
What nonsense are you talking about?

585
00:42:05,383 --> 00:42:07,213
It's quite good actually.

586
00:42:07,887 --> 00:42:09,887
At least you have someone
to pick fight with at home.

587
00:42:09,928 --> 00:42:11,228
You guys can take care of each other too.

588
00:42:11,792 --> 00:42:14,002
It's better than living alone like me.

589
00:42:14,715 --> 00:42:15,675
Mr. Zhuo is back in the office.

590
00:42:15,716 --> 00:42:17,036
He wants to have dinner
with you tonight.

591
00:42:17,077 --> 00:42:18,057
I have to go.

592
00:42:18,454 --> 00:42:20,274
Why are you in a rush?

593
00:42:22,009 --> 00:42:23,259
Slow down.
